<promed@promedmail.org>
[We had trouble in deciding on a suitable title for such a mixed report,
but FMD was listed first, as it is a more important problem than
brucellosis. Thailand reported extensive outbreaks of FMD in 2001 and 2000.
- Mod.MHJ]
